&lt;li&gt;Manage day-to-day relationships with US and APJ PR agencies, including planning, pitching, deliverables, and performance tracking.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop and maintain a strategic PR calendar aligned to product launches, campaigns, events, and key market moments.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner with the EMEA PR Manager to ensure global alignment and consistency of messaging, while tailoring execution for regional relevance.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with the social media manager to amplify earned media, integrate PR into broader campaigns, and maximize cross-channel impact.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build and execute executive thought leadership programs, including bylines, media commentary, podcasts, and speaking opportunities on topics such as AI, agentic AI, verified trust, fraud, and digital identity.&lt;/li&gt;
